grail.canonicalQuery:
fetch dt.entity.host
| expand managementZone = managementZones
| fields managementZone, entity.name
| summarize by:{managementZone, entity.name}, count = count()
| summarize by:{entity.name}, unique_appcodes = sum(count)
| sort unique_appcodes desc
| limit 100000

fetch dt.entity.host
| expand managementZone = managementZones
| fields managementZone, entity.name
| summarize by:{managementZone, entity.name}, count = count()
| summarize by:{entity.name}, unique_appcodes = sum(count)
| sort unique_appcodes desc
| limit 100000
| join 
	[
		fetch dt.entity.host
		| expand managementZone = managementZones
		| fields managementZone, entity.name, customHostMetadata, monitoringMode, memoryTotal, lifetime
		| fieldsAdd customHostMetadata, monitoringMode, Memory_GB = memoryTotal / (1024.0 * 1024 * 1024), lifetime, managementZone
		| fields entity.name, monitoringMode = if(contains(entity.name, ""), "FULL_STACK", else:monitoringMode), Memory_GB, lifetime, managementZone
		| fieldsAdd managementZone, HostUnits_Used = if(monitoringMode == "FULL_STACK" AND Memory_GB > 8, ceil(Memory_GB / 16.0), else:if(monitoringMode == "INFRASTRUCTURE" AND Memory_GB >= 64, 1, else:0.5))
		| summarize by:{entity.name, managementZone}, `Total HU` = sum(HostUnits_Used)
	], on:{entity.name}
| summarize by:{Tag = right.managementZone}, `Average HU` = sum(`right.Total HU` / unique_appcodes)

| append[
  timeseries {
    operand1 = sum(dt.service.request.count, rate: 1m),
    operand2 = sum(dt.service.request.failure_count, rate: 1m)
  }, by:{dt.entity.service}, bins: 60, filter: dt.entity.service == "SERVICE-F0E536B1037E6AE0", nonempty: true
  | fieldsAdd successfulRequests_timeseries = operand1[] - operand2[] 
  | fieldsRemove operand1, operand2 | fieldsAdd metricName = "Successful requests"]
